      • getID

        public java.lang.String getID(A obj)
        Description copied from interface: IndexedProducer
        Generate the default text identifier of the client object for contexts where the type is unambiguous. This is used in urls and html inputs. Normally this should generate the String representation of the integer id. if it generates anything else the IndexedProducer should implement ParseFactory to be able to parse the alternative form.
